CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

August 5, 2010

[Cite as 08/05/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-3583.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

1990-1927. State v. Lorraine.

Trumbull App. No. 3838. This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing of Luigia Tenuta’s motion for extraordinary consideration of fees/expenses and application for attorney fees.

It is ordered by the court that the motion is denied and the application for attorney fees is denied.
